  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the effect of vitamin D supplementation in the form of Alfacalcidol on
      the the pulmonary function of adult asthmatic Egyptian patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Asthmatic patients are recruited and divided into two groups. One receives Alfacalcidol
      beside their normal medications while the other acts as a control group receiving the normal
      asthma medication.

      Both groups are followed up for four months.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
